  <brief_title>Effect of Monosodium Glutamate Supplementation on Gastric Emptying and Postprandial Nitrogen Kinetics</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Monosodium Glutamate on Gastric Emptying and Postprandial Nitrogen in Healthy Volunteers</official_title>
